### ===================== CATEGORY MANAGEMENT =====================

### 1. Create main category
POST {{url}}/categories/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fresh Produce",
  "description": "Fresh fruits",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/images/fresh-produce.jpg"

}

### 2. Create subcategory
POST {{url}}/categories/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fruits",
  "description": "Fresh vegetables",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/images/fruits.jpg"
}

### 3. Create another subcategory
POST {{url}}/categories/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vegetables",
  "description": "Fresh seasonal vegetables",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/images/vegetables.jpg"
}

### 4. Get all categories
GET {{url}}/categories/all

### 5. Get active categories only
GET {{url}}/categories/active

### 6. Get main categories (no parent)
GET {{url}}/categories/main

### 7. Get categories with products
GET {{url}}/categories/with-products

### 8. Get specific category by ID
GET {{url}}/categories/1

### 9. Get category by slug
GET {{url}}/categories/slug/fresh-produce

### 10. Update category
PATCH {{url}}/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fresh Produce & Organics",
  "description": "Fresh fruits, vegetables and organic produce",
  "sort_order": 1
}

### 11. Get category statistics
GET {{url}}/categories/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 12. Delete category (only if no products/subcategories)
DELETE {{url}}/categories/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}